## PointSeries type

A `PointSeries` is a unique structure that represents dots on a chart.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type PointSeries = ExpressionValueBoxed<'pointseries', {
    columns: PointSeriesColumns;
    rows: PointSeriesRow[];
}>;
```
